value.0: Your message is inscribed on this paper. You may post it on any bulletin board.

A diabolical crossbow; with each pull of the trigger a flaming bolt springs forth, easily burning through the flesh of a foe. Used commonly by assassins, it enchances the wearers sight of hearing and vision, while being sturdy built enough to give it extreme precision and might.
This woman appears to be looking for something valuable.

Value.value: Yes! This is perfect! Er... Flawless, I mean! Thank you very much. Here's the Enhanced Recall Stone, as promised. My associate will tell you more about these stones, if you like.

I am looking for Flawless Mythals for my research into the events which led to the creation of the crystals. In exchange, I offer a valuable Enhanced Recall Stone, which you can use in addition to the usual Recall Stones. I'll exchange as many times as you want!
